alue>done</value></item><item><label>Not Done</label><value>not</value></item></select1><select1 appearance="list-nolabel" ref="/data/intro/step1"><label>Wash hands with soap and put on disposable gloves and apron</label><item><label>Done</label><value>done</value></item><item><label>Not Done</label><value>not</value></item></select1><select1 appearance="list-nolabel" ref="/data/intro/step2"><label>Prepare the solution at the required temperature</label><item><label>Done</label><value>done</value></item><item><label>Not Done</label><value>not</value></item></select1><select1 appearance="list-nolabel" ref="/data/intro/step3"><label>Attach the tubing and the rectal tube with tunnel , pour the solution in it and check for leakage</label><item><label>Done</label><value>done</value></item><item><label>Not Done</label><value>not</value></item></select1><select1 appearance="list-nolabel" ref="/data/intro/step4"><label>Lubricate the tip of rectal tube about 4 inches</label><item><label>Done</label><value>done</value></item><item><label>Not Done</label><value>not</value></item></select1><select1 appearance="list-nolabel" ref="/data/intro/step5"><label>Fill the tunnel with the solution and expel air from the funnel , allowing a small amount of fluid to run into kidney tray. Pinch the tray</label><item><label>Done</label><value>done</value></item><item><label>Not Done</label><value>not</value></item></select1><select1 appearance="list-nolabel" ref="/data/intro/step6"><label>Separate the patients buttocks to visualize the anus clearly and insert the tip about 4 inches while patient exhales</label><item><label>Done</label><value>done</value></item><item><label>Not Done</label><value>not</value></item></select1><select1 appearance="list-nolabel" ref="/data/intro/step7"><label>Lower the funnel below the level of rectum</label><item><label>Done</label><value>done</value></item><item><label>Not Done</label><value>not</value></item></select1><select1 appearance="list-nolabel" ref="/data/intro/step8"><label>Raise the funnel and allow the fluid to run in continue to pour more fluid into the funnel before funnel is empty</label><item><label>Done</label><value>done</value></item><item><label>Not Done</label><value>not</value></item></select1><select1 appearance="list-nolabel" ref="/data/intro/step9"><label>When 200 to 300 ml of fluid has gone in pinch the tube before the funnel is completely empty and invert it over the bucket and syphon off the fluid</label><item><label>Done</label><value>done</value></item><item><label>Not Done</label><value>not</value></item></select1><select1 appearance="list-nolabel" ref="/data/intro/step10"><label>When the return flow ceases turns the funnel upright and pours more solution . Lower the funnel until air from the tube has been expelled . then raise the funnel a nd repeat the fluid to run in, continue to pour more fluid in funnel before funnel is empty</label><item><label>Done</label><value>done</value></item><item><label>Not Done</label><value>not</value></item></select1><select1 appearance="list-nolabel" ref="/data/intro/step11"><label>Continue the procedure until all the fluid ordered has been given or till the return of flow is clear</label><item><label>Done</label><value>done</value></item><item><label>Not Done</label><value>not</value></item></select1><select1 appearance="list-nolabel" ref="/data/intro/step12"><label>Temporarily stop the procedure if the patient develops any discomfort</label><item><label>Done</label><value>done</value></item><item><label>Not Done</label><value>not</value></item></select1><select1 appearance="list-nolabel" ref="/data/intro/step13"><label>Gently remove the rectal tube by pulling through 3-4 layers of rag pieces or gauze pieces</label><item><label>Done</label><value>done</value></item><item><label>Not Done</label><value>not</value></item></select1><select1 appearance="list-nolabel" ref="/data/intro/step14"><label>Discard the rag pieces in paper bag , pace funnel with the tubing in kidney tray</label><item><label>Done</label><value>done</value></item><item><label>Not Done</label><value>not</value></item></select1></group></h:body></h:html>